text: Stoyan Stoyanov (born 25 October 1931) is a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics, the 1956 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics
